        {
          "title": "Lightbathing (22769737922)",
          "description": "We went for a little hike at Koyodai near Lake Saiko, Yamanashi Prefecture, Japan. It may have been a bit early as most of the leaves are still green. It was also cloudy that day so Mount Fuji was hiding behind the clouds. My dream view of Mount Fuji along with the trees of Aokigahara Forest was a failure :( But we decided to continue walking until we reached this place, Sankodai. For me, this is a much better location than Koyodai as it is wide open with very few trees obstructing the view. We were provided with this view, as the clouds parted a bit letting glorious sunrays shine over the scenery.",
